        <updateDate>2013-04-18T19:01:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Medical Research Protection Act of 2013 - Amends the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985 (Gramm-Rudman-Hollings Act) to exempt the National Institutes of Health (NIH) from any sequestration ordered by the President for FY2013.</p> <p>Directs the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) for FY2013 to lower the amount calculated for a sequestration by the amount for which NIH would have been reduced if it were not exempt from sequestration.</p> <ul> <ul> </ul> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
